              Within reason, I might consider. Please note however that I do not add random strangers into my account, so it would be much appreciated if you first send me a message explaining how you found my account and why you wish to add me as a friend on that website. I will not acknowledge any requests otherwise. Feel free to +watch my account on dA and follow my Cure account, however--they're mostly artistic sites.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="loud">Why are there no photos of you in the About Me page?</h3>
