              For privacy concerns. Although I've uploaded several artistic photographs in the portfolio for previewing purposes only. You may navigate to them <%= link_to "here", port_cos_path%> if you wish. Moving your cursor over the images will also give you additional information about the photos, if only minimal. If that does not satisfy you, you may look for my third-party accounts <%= link_to "outside", main_contact_path %> this website.
          </p>
          
